Package velinov.java.vrep.objects

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ObjectUpdater
    Defines an VrepObject updater, that updates the objects with their dynamic simulation parameters.
    VrepObject
    an interface describing a V-REP scene object.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbsObjectUpdater
    An abstract implementation of ObjectUpdater.
    AbsVrepObject
    an abstract implementation of VrepObject.
    ProximitySensor
    Represents VrepObject of type VrepObjectType#PROXIMITY_SENSOR.
    Shape
    Represents a Shape VrepObject.
    VrepObjectName
    Represents a VrepObject name, which consists of a base name and an index.

    VrepObjectType
    An Enum describing the different types of VrepObjects.
